"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:42:07.000Z","msg":"關於沈教授20點之我見<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2035226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2035226</a>"},{"pid":"e7159518a2d8dcb8733a0a6638c42550fcd0f793","tid":2035791,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:49:36.000Z","msg":"港股收市升432點美團急升逾一成<br />\n26.05.2020 16:28<br />\n<br />\n港股跟隨內地及亞太股市上升，恒生指數高開246點，其後升幅擴大至逾500點，高見23481點，收報23384點，升432點，升幅1.9%，成交額1074億元。國企指數收報9595點，升129點，升幅1.3%。<br />\n<br />\n本地地產股有反彈，恒基地產(<a href=\"http://00012.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00012.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=9886774e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00012.HK</a>)終止連續4日跌勢，升近5%，報28.25元，升1.3元，是升幅最大藍籌。新地(<a href=\"http://00016.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00016.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e4c4813b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00016.HK</a>)升近4%，報92.6元。九倉置業(<a href=\"http://01997.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01997.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e3a4a4aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01997.HK</a>)升3%，報29.05元。<br />\n<br />\n新經濟股造好，美團點評(<a href=\"http://03690.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03690.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=68e1215a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03690.HK</a>)業績後被券商上調目標價，股價再破頂，以全日最高位收市，升逾一成，報138.9元，升13.1元。騰訊(<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=31bf6317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>)升2%，報425.4元。阿里巴巴(<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=688294a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>)升逾1%，報201元。<br />\n<br />\n信德集團創辦人、澳博榮譽主席何鴻燊病逝，信德集團(<a href=\"http://00242.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00242.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=c5065326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00242.HK</a>)股價下午異動，曾急升兩成半，高見3.22元，收市升近22%，報3.12元，升0.56元。另外，澳博(<a href=\"http://00880.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00880.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=78cdfc2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00880.HK</a>)升7%，報8.84元。其他家族相關股亦造好，美高梅中國(<a href=\"http://02282.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02282.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e1357cc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02282.HK</a>)升5%，報9.37元；新濠國際(<a href=\"http://00200.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00200.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=368c6c79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00200.HK</a>)升5%，報15.02元；澳門勵駿(<a href=\"http://01680.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01680.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=523ef73b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01680.HK</a>)升6%，報1.05元。"},{"pid":"921c76542897aaa63e2230a77223f05dbe75f6d2","tid":2035791,"uid":82301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:52:52.000Z","msg":"最唔明係美團呢啲垃圾都可以爆升"},{"pid":"663bc1e46b1fa8da67b11ba4f94003437873a9d0","tid":2035791,"uid":20368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:52:53.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n國安法對大戶有咩影響？<br />\n專心炒股撚會拉你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得連登仔先驚"},{"pid":"7e74a379202f29aea13046dbc497ffa7328446ad","tid":2035791,"uid":118226,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd096ecd2bd07f239cb9b9c4908c259bbf66f788","tid":2035791,"uid":78304,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"爺你老母，得七十幾年嘅國家叫佢做阿爺？"},"citedBy":1,"re